==English==
===Noun===
'''[[needle]] [[in]] a [[haystack]]'''
# Something that is [[difficult]] or [[impossible]] to locate; something impossibly [[complex]] or [[intractable]].
#:''You'll never find the paper you need on her desk.  It's a '''needle in a haystack'''.''

